text"},{"preciseIdentifier":"s:22ComposableArchitecture7ReducerP","text":"Reducer","identifier":"doc:\/\/ComposableArchitecture\/documentation\/ComposableArchitecture\/Reducer","kind":"typeIdentifier"},{"text":"\n","kind":"text"}]}]},{"parameters":[{"name":"toStackState","content":[{"inlineContent":[{"type":"text","text":"A writable key path from parent state to a stack of destination state."}],"type":"paragraph"}]},{"name":"toStackAction","content":[{"type":"paragraph","inlineContent":[{"type":"text","text":"A case path from parent action to a stack action."}]}]},{"name":"destination","content":[{"type":"paragraph","inlineContent":[{"text":"A reducer that will be invoked with destination actions against elements of","type":"text"},{"text":" ","type":"text"},{"text":"destination state.","type":"text"}]}]},{"name":"fileID","content":[{"type":"paragraph","inlineContent":[{"type":"text","text":"The fileID."}]}]},{"name":"filePath","content":[{"type":"paragraph","inlineContent":[{"type":"text","text":"The filePath."}]}]},{"name":"line","content":[{"type":"paragraph","inlineContent":[{"text":"The line.","type":"text"}]}]},{"name":"column","content":[{"inlineContent":[{"text":"The column.","type":"text"}],"type":"paragraph"}]}],"kind":"parameters"},{"kind":"content","content":[{"type":"heading","level":2,"text":"Return Value","anchor":"return-value"},{"type":"paragraph","inlineContent":[{"type":"text","text":"A reducer that combines the destination reducer with the parent reducer."}]}]},{"kind":"content","content":[{"anchor":"discussion","level":2,"type":"heading","text":"Discussion"},{"type":"paragraph","inlineContent":[{"text":"This version of ","type":"text"},{"type":"codeVoice","code":"forEach"},{"text":" works when the parent domain holds onto the child domain using","type":"text"},{"text":" ","type":"text"},{"identifier":"doc:\/\/ComposableArchitecture\/documentation\/ComposableArchitecture\/StackState","type":"reference","isActive":true},{"text":" and ","type":"text"},{"identifier":"doc:\/\/ComposableArchitecture\/documentation\/ComposableArchitecture\/StackAction","type":"reference","isActive":true},{"text":".","type":"text"}]},{"type":"paragraph","inlineContent":[{"type":"text","text":"For example, if a parent feature models a navigation stack of child features using the"},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"reference","identifier":"doc:\/\/ComposableArchitecture\/documentation\/ComposableArchitecture\/StackState","isActive":true},{"type":"text","text":" and "},{"type":"reference","identifier":"doc:\/\/ComposableArchitecture\/documentation\/ComposableArchitecture\/StackAction","isActive":true},{"type":"text","text":" types, then it can perform its core logic "},{"type":"emphasis","inlineContent":[{"type":"text","text":"and"}]},{"type":"text","text":" the logic"},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"text","text":"of each child feature using the "},{"type":"codeVoice","code":"forEach"},{"type":"text","text":" operator:"}]},{"code":["@Reducer","struct ParentFeature {","  struct State {","    var path = StackState<Path.State>()","    \/\/ ...","  }","  enum Action {","    case path(StackActionOf<Path>)","    \/\/ ...","  }","  var body: some ReducerOf<Self> {","    Reduce { state, action in","      \/\/ Core parent logic","    }","    .forEach(\\.path, action: \\.path) {","      Path()","    }","  }","}"],"type":"codeListing","syntax":"swift"},{"type":"paragraph","inlineContent":[{"type":"text","text":"The "},{"code":"forEach","type":"codeVoice"},{"type":"text","text":" operator does a number of things to make integrating parent and child features"},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"text","text":"ergonomic and enforce correctness:"}]},{"items":[{"content":[{"type":"paragraph","inlineContent":[{"type":"text","text":"It forces a specific order of operations for the child and parent features:"}]},{"type":"unorderedList","items":[{"content":[{"type":"paragraph","inlineContent":[{"type":"text","text":"When a "},{"type":"reference","identifier":"doc:\/\/ComposableArchitecture\/documentation\/ComposableArchitecture\/StackAction\/element(id:action:)","isActive":true},{"type":"text","text":" action is sent it runs the"},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"text","text":"child first, and then the parent. If the order was reversed, then it would be possible"},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"text","text":"for the parent feature to "},{"type":"codeVoice","code":"nil"},{"type":"text","text":" out the child state, in which case the child feature"},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"text","text":"would not be able to react to that action. That can cause subtle bugs."}]}]},{"content":[{"type":"paragraph","inlineContent":[{"type":"text","text":"When a "},{"identifier":"doc:\/\/ComposableArchitecture\/documentation\/ComposableArchitecture\/StackAction\/popFrom(id:)","isActive":true,"type":"reference"},{"type":"text","text":" action is sent it runs the parent feature"},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"text","text":"before the child state is popped off the stack. This gives the parent feature an"},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"text","text":"opportunity to inspect the child state one last time before the state is removed."}]}]},{"content":[{"type":"paragraph","inlineContent":[{"text":"When a ","type":"text"},{"isActive":true,"type":"reference","identifier":"doc:\/\/ComposableArchitecture\/documentation\/ComposableArchitecture\/StackAction\/push(id:state:)"},{"text":" action is sent it runs the parent feature","type":"text"},{"text":" ","type":"text"},{"text":"after the child state is appended to the stack. This gives the parent feature an","type":"text"},{"text":" ","type":"text"},{"text":"opportunity to make extra mutations to the state after it has been added.","type":"text"}]}]}]}]},{"content":[{"type":"paragraph","inlineContent":[{"text":"It automatically cancels all child effects when it detects the child’s state is removed","type":"text"},{"text":" ","type":"text"},{"text":"from the stack","type":"text"}]}]},{"content":[{"type":"paragraph","inlineContent":[{"text":"It gives the child feature access to the ","type":"text"},{"isActive":true,"type":"reference","identifier":"doc:\/\/ComposableArchitecture\/documentation\/ComposableArchitecture\/DismissEffect"},{"text":" dependency, which allows the","type":"text"},{"text":" ","type":"text"},{"text":"child feature to dismiss itself without communicating with the parent.","type":"text"}]}]}],"type":"unorderedList"}]}],"abstract":[{"type":"text","text":"Embeds a child reducer in a parent domain that works on elements of a navigation stack in"},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"text","text":"parent state."}],"sections":[],"hierarchy":{"paths":[["doc:\/\/ComposableArchitecture\/documentation\/ComposableArchitecture","doc:\/\/ComposableArchitecture\/documentation\/ComposableArchitecture\/Reducer","doc:\/\/ComposableArchitecture\/documentation\/ComposableArchitecture\/Scope","doc:\/\/ComposableArchitecture\/documentation\/ComposableArchitecture\/Scope\/Reducer-Implementations"]]},"metadata":{"roleHeading":"Instance Method","title":"forEach(_:action:destination:fileID:filePath:line:column:)","extendedModule":"ComposableArchitecture","modules":[{"name":"ComposableArchitecture"}],"externalID":"s:22ComposableArchitecture7ReducerPAAE7forEach_6action11destination6fileID0H4Path4line6columnQrs011WritableKeyJ0Cy5StateQzAA05StackO0Vyqd__GG_s0nJ0Cy13CasePathsCore0Q0Vy6ActionQzGAWyAA0pT0Oyqd__qd_0_GGGqd_1_yXEs12StaticStringVA5_S2utAMQyd_1_Rsd__AXQyd_1_Rsd_0_AaBRd_1_r1_lF::SYNTHESIZED::s:22ComposableArchitecture5ScopeV","fragments":[{"text":"func","kind":"keyword"},{"text":" ","kind":"text"},{"text":"forEach","kind":"identifier"},{"text":"<","kind":"text"},{"text":"DestinationState","kind":"genericParameter"},{"text":", ","kind":"text"},{"text":"DestinationAction","kind":"genericParameter"},{"text":", ","kind":"text"},{"text":"Destination","kind":"genericParameter"},{"text":">(","kind":"text"},{"preciseIdentifier":"s:s15Wr